  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fighters returned to Colombo on the 30th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the activists are scheduled to return to Colombo on the 30th.",
        "The interim budget speech is scheduled to be presented by the President on the 30th. The intelligence agencies have reported to the government that the organizations involved in the struggle have already decided to come to Colombo and hold demonstrations on that day.",
        "The activists came to Colombo a few weeks ago to protest against the government. At this time, the security forces dispersed the people by firing tear gas and water cannons."
      ],
